216 bool VTKField::hasAllMetaData() const{
217 
218  bool allData(true);
219 
220  allData &= m_name != "undefined" ;
221  allData &= m_dataType != VTKDataType::UNDEFINED ;
222  allData &= m_location != VTKLocation::UNDEFINED ;
223  allData &= m_codification != VTKFormat::UNDEFINED ;
224  allData &= m_fieldType != VTKFieldType::UNDEFINED ;
225  allData &= m_streamer != nullptr ;
226 
227  return allData;
228 
229 }

247 void VTKField::read( std::fstream &str, uint64_t entries, uint8_t components ) const{
